title: Argentina vs Brazil | Matchday 14 Highlights | CONMEBOL South American World Cup Qualifiers
author: fubo Sports
description:
Argentina and Brazil played out a feisty 0-0 draw, which saw the hosts stretch their unbeaten run to 27 games, almost certainly securing their spot at next year's World Cup, whilst Tite’s men maintained their six-point advantage at the summit of the group - with a spot in Qatar already assured.
